n
a_{i},(i=0,1,\cdots,n-1)
\{0,1,2,\cdots,n-1\}
k=0,1,2,\cdots,n-1
\left(\sum_{i=0}^{n-1}a_{i}\cos{\dfrac{2k\pi i}{n}}\right)^2\le (n^2-1)\left(\sum_{i=0}^{n-1}a_{i}\sin{\dfrac{2k\pi i}{n}}\right)^2
\Longleftrightarrow \left(\sum_{i=0}^{n-1}a_{i}\cos{\dfrac{2k\pi i}{n}}\right)^2+\left(\sum_{i=0}^{n-1}a_{i}\sin{\dfrac{2k\pi i}{n}}\right)^2\le n^2\left(\sum_{i=0}^{n-1}a_{i}\sin{\dfrac{2k\pi i}{n}}\right)^2
